ttp_template:
<group name="ont_id_ont_port_id_ont_port_type_speed_mbps_duplex_link_state_ring_status">
       {{ONT_ID | re("\\d+")}} {{ONT_PORT_ID | re("\\d+")}} {{ONT_PORT_TYPE}} {{SPEED_MBPS}} {{DUPLEX}} {{LINK_STATE | ORPHRASE}} {{RING_STATUS | ORPHRASE}} 
</group>
<group name="ont_id_ont_port_id_ont_port_type_link_state_ring_status">
       {{ONT_ID | re("\\d+")}} {{ONT_PORT_ID | re("\\d+")}} {{ONT_PORT_TYPE}} - - {{LINK_STATE | ORPHRASE}} {{RING_STATUS | ORPHRASE}} 
</group>
textfsm_template:
Value Key ONT_ID (\d+)
Value ONT_PORT_ID (\d+)
Value ONT_PORT_TYPE (\S+)
Value SPEED_MBPS (\S+)
Value DUPLEX (\S+)
Value LINK_STATE (up|down)
Value RING_STATUS (\S+)

Start
  ^\s+ONT-ID\s+ONT\s*ONT\s*Speed\(Mbps\)\s*Duplex\s*LinkState\s*RingStatus\s*$$
  ^\s+port-ID\s*Port-type\s*$$
  ^\s+${ONT_ID}\s+${ONT_PORT_ID}\s+${ONT_PORT_TYPE}\s*(-|${SPEED_MBPS})\s*(-|${DUPLEX})\s*${LINK_STATE}\s*${RING_STATUS} -> Record
  ^\s+-
  ^. -> Error
